    <StepperContext.Provider value={{ activeStep, orientation }}>
      <div
        data-slot="stepper"
        data-orientation={orientation}
        className={cn(
          "group/stepper flex flex-col gap-4",
          className
        )}
        {...props}
      >
        {children}
      </div>
    </StepperContext.Provider>
  )
}
```

And the demo uses a wrapper for items:

```typescript
